'''cosmetic'''  (''plural:'' [[cosmetics]])

#An substance applied to enhance the external color or texture of the [[skin]], e.g. [[lipstick]], [[eyeshadow]], [[eyeliner]]; [[makeup]]. 
#A [[feature]] existing only on the surface.

